{"type": "article", "id": 28883, "title": "王大仁主管自家品牌，以及，推荐一款春夏双肩包｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-06-29T12:27:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12089, "name": "女装"}, {"id": 3975, "name": "实验室"}, {"id": 9879, "name": "胶囊系列"}, {"id": 4780, "name": "快闪店"}, {"id": 29556, "name": "鞋履品牌"}, {"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 11592, "name": "夏季"}, {"id": 3126, "name": "牛仔"}, {"id": 2837, "name": "DKNY"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 29557, "name": "Aquazzura"}, {"id": 2634, "name": "Under Armour"}, {"id": 3078, "name": "Max Mara"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607031236243obWtmMFP6RzaHyN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/alexander-wang-named-ceo-of-alexander-wang-inc-10474058/\"><b>Alexander Wang 担任个人品牌 CEO 兼董事长</b></a>｜2005 年创立了个人同名品牌并担任创意总监的 Alexander Wang，近日宣布出任公司董事长兼 CEO，即刻生效。此前由母亲 Ying Wang  及嫂子 Aimie Wang 担任董事长及 CEO 的职位。其它高层变动包括 Mary Wang 担任高级副总裁，过去担任 DKNY 总裁，她将在 Alexander Wang 掌管全球运营业务并直接向 Alexander 报告。而另一位 Caroline Wang 则是 Alexander Wang 的直系亲属，将加入公司担任行政副主席，此前在 IBM 担任亚太地区市场、信息技术及业务转型部门的副总裁。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/ready-to-wear-sportswear/max-mara-group-lainch-two-new-fashion-brands-10473204/\"><b>Max Mara 集团将推出两个新品牌</b></a>｜意大利时装集团 Max Mara 将推出两个新的女装品牌 Aiim 和 Tresophie ，将从 2017 年 1 月开始在意大利、法国、英国、西班牙售卖，美国地区则从 2017 秋季系列开始。Aiim 专注于针织系列，均价在 160 欧元（即 176 美元左右），Tresophie 则更正式、优雅，更适合参加晚宴、庆典、派对等，价格在 280 欧元（即 308 美元）左右。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/intimates-activewear/under-armour-opens-baltimore-lab-manufacturing-design-innovation-10474270/\"><b>Under Armour 开设制造、设计创新实验室</b></a>｜Under Armour  近日在品牌发源地巴尔的摩，开设 35000 平方英尺面积的新实验室 UA Lighthouse，为了制造及设计方面的创新。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/specialty-stores/aquazzura-opens-pop-up-store-in-east-hampton-10474841/\"><b>Aquazzura 开快闪店</b></a>｜奢侈鞋履品牌 Aquazzura 在纽约东汉普顿地区（East Hampton）开设持续到九月的快闪店，售卖春季及早秋系列。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Herschel-Supply-partners-with-Major-League-Baseball,708059.html\"><b>Herschel Supply 与 MLB 合作</b></a>｜温哥华包袋品牌 Herschel Supply 与美国职业棒球大联盟（MLB）合作，推出多伦多蓝鸟队系列包袋，只在加拿大及官网售卖。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123607Xfexr7qzo4pLNs5O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59215686\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/gucci-to-unveil-womens-capsule-collection-10474741/\">Gucci 推出一个女装胶囊系列 Gucci Garden</a>，将从 7 月 5 日开始，仅在 Gucci 官网贩售：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123608OzesboM1J2W3QNwt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123608876laBEtMskVQiUY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81835938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123609yXwDOPte9iQYBmNE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123609E6cokLW7giXVxRb1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123610oYMOHrbJhRui3Zck.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123610YErLSM2ZJXUBbK09.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">如果喜欢浅色牛仔和更清爽的风格，可以看看 <a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/shows-reviews/gallery/karen-walker-resort-2017-10474431/#!24/karen-walker-resort-2017-24/\">Karen Walker 的 2017 早春度假系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031236113I80O9nkfgJQSbxE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123611X3E8UpkcJTy9KZzm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123611IaPzBSCxgNW9Dk7T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123612yG9QgzAfSEH5vj80.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123612S6eHr1jLflpCZdFT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">巴黎以街头服饰起家的品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/pigalle-spring-summer-2017-menswear-collection\"> Pigalle 发布 2017 春夏系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123613oJABD1NkfrTIud2g.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75123885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123613kqTXPIDv5mZHgAr9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75123885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123614IX9NnkceWYbVR1hu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75123885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123615V4KfCgsQ6Y0vNXib.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75123885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2